title: Bonkers and beautiful
review: Somehow I just don't think this will be shown on TV in a holiday viewing period. Utterly bonkers, but beautiful.

title: Mamma Mia on speed
review: Slick, polished and hugely gripping, it doesn't slow down for a second. Doesn't really touch on key theme of addiction and brushes away living life sober, but hey, its a good film WTF!
